  "time_ut": 1656424696,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbe \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Request made by the Attorney General",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Airport Services Company, through the Attorney General's Department, today (28) filed a transfer letter in the Colombo Commercial High Court seeking the dismissal of the case filed against Russia's Aeroflot aircraft.",
        "Colombo Commercial High Court Judge Harsha Sethunga had on the 6th issued an order suspending the execution of the restraining order issued against the Russian Aeroflot aircraft.",
        "The aforesaid order was issued after taking into consideration the facts presented by the parties including the Attorney General that the restraining order was obtained by misleading the court and misrepresenting the facts.",
        "Additional Solicitor General Presidential Counsel Sumathi Dharmawardena, appearing on behalf of the 2nd respondent Airport Services Company, requested the court to dismiss the petition as the Russian Aeroflot flight had left the court premises.",
        "Dr. Lasantha Hettiarachchi, appearing for the Russian airline, demanded a possible expeditious date for the investigation into the matter as Aeroflot has suspended operations in Sri Lanka.",
        "Considering the facts, Colombo Commercial High Court Judge Harsha Sethunga adjourned the case to July 5.",
        "On June 2, the Colombo Chamber of Commerce issued a restraining order preventing Russian Aeroflot aircraft from taking off from Sri Lankan territory, in response to a request from Celestial Aviation Trading Limited in Ireland.",
        "It is noteworthy that Celestial Aviation Trading Ltd. of Ireland received the injunction for failure to comply with the terms of the lease agreement between the two parties of Russia Aeroflot Airlines."
      ],
